2015-04-17  Michael Wiegand <michael.wiegand@greenbone.net>

	Preparing the openvas-manager 5.0.10 release.

	* CHANGES: Updated.

	* CMakeLists.txt: Raise minimum required version of openvas-libraries
	to 7.0.10.

	* INSTALL: Update version requirements to match change to
	CMakeLists.txt.

