	(READ_PROTOCOL_TIMEOUT, FROM_BUFFER_SIZE): New defines.  From oxpd.h.

	* src/openvasmd.c: Remove oxpd.h.
	(serve_client): Just serve OMP, instead of doing a protocol check.

	* src/oxpd.c, src/oxpd.h: Remove.

