	(serve_client, fork_connection_for_schedular): Pass disabled_commands to
	omp handlers.
	(cleanup): Free disabled_commands too.
	(update_or_rebuild_nvt_cache): Add dummay serve_omp arg.
	(main): Add --disable-cmds.

