	DELETE_SCHEDULE handling.

2010-03-22  Matthew Mundell <matthew.mundell@greenbone.net>

	* src/omp.c (buffer_schedules_xml): Add tasks that use the schedular to
	response.

	* src/manage_sql.c (schedule_iterator_schedule)
