	* src/omp.c (omp_xml_handle_end_element): In CLIENT_AUTHENTICATE respond
	with error code on error.

	* src/CMakeLists.txt (TEMP): Split into LIB_TEMP and HEADER_TEMP.
	(manage): Pass openvas headers.

